      <title>房地产危机推高房价，澳联储将延长加息暂停期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/rba-set-to-extend-rate-pause-as-housing-crisis-props-up-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚创纪录的家庭债务是澳大利亚央行谨慎采取紧缩政策的一个关键因素，现在住房问题已成为澳大利亚央行在宽松周期中成为异类并在本周维持利率不变的重要考虑因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/rba-set-to-extend-rate-pause-as-housing-crisis-props-up-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理关注企业税，警告债务问题“严重”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-eyes-business-taxes-warns-debt-in-grave-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶表示，新政府可能会增加大企业和富人的税收，以修复失控的预算赤字并保持债券市场的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-eyes-business-taxes-warns-debt-in-grave-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:44:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷或实施限电措施应对夏季用电需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/argentina-would-implement-power-cuts-to-cope-with-summer-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于天气预报显示南半球今年夏季气温将升高，消费者将不得不打开空调，阿根廷计划采取计划性断电措施来应对电力需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/argentina-would-implement-power-cuts-to-cope-with-summer-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员需要新的股市策略来应对降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/traders-need-a-new-stock-market-playbook-for-these-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储现在已开始降息，华尔街交易员在股市押注时面临着一个独特的挑战：历史不再具有指导作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/traders-need-a-new-stock-market-playbook-for-these-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 13:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
